snippet.title: Warframe - Game Awards Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/warframe-ps4/

Play between now and February 1, 2017 for a chance to win a Prime PlayStation®4 Pro Setup!

https://www.warframe.com/giveaway

You are Tenno, an ancient warrior, a master of gun and blade. You wield the mighty Warframes and command their awesome powers. Forge your weapons. Gather like-minded Tenno and take the fight back to the Grineer. The Origin System needs you once again.
 
Are you ready?

Rated Mature: Blood & Gore; Violence
